transcripts.text: Welcome to Iceland.  Oh my God, this is amazing.  Welcome to India.  This is amazing.  Life is so beautiful.  I'm so grateful.  This is the best sunset I've ever seen in my life.

A very long time ago, I had a dream and envision on a random night at 4 a.m On that random night, I decided that I was going to be a travel blogger.  I figured I would travel the world, take beautiful pictures, do extraordinary things, make all my wildest dreams come true, and help inspire the world to do the very same thing.  When I started that journey, I had absolutely no idea what that entailed.  I've dedicated the last five years working on that dream.  Sleepless nights, every second.
